                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   History - Service                                           You may look up a history of a repair three ways, by customers phone number, by serial number and by "Any Search"

Phone Number - Enter the 7 digit of the phone number in the search filed and press the F3 Key. All repairs ever entered under this phone number will be displayed in a list. (Quick Search)

Serial Number - Enter the serial number in the search field and press the F4 key. All repairs even saved to history will be displayed in a list. (Quick Search)

Any Search - Enter what you want to look up in the search field and press the F5 key. Then select the year you want to search in. See screen promtps.  All files found with this search will be displayed in a list. (Not Quick Search)

Click on the list to see brief details on the selection. Double click or highlight and press ENTER key to see Full details.

ESC key to clear search.                                                                                                                                               Open Repair                                                 You can open a repair three ways.

Quickest is by entering the claim number. The file will open up instantly.
If the claim number is not found, a list will display from that number on. Click on the claim number you want to review, ESC key will clear screen.

Name Search - Enter the beginning part of the customer name as it was entered as a new repair. If you enter a customer as 'Smith, Pete", then enter smith in the search field and press ENTER. A list will display from Smith on. Click on the name you wish to review.  ESC key will clear screen.

Any Search - Enter what you want to seach for in an open repair. This could be an address, model, serial #, anything you entered in the repair. A list will display the results. Use your up/down arrow key to scroll the list. Click on the file you want to review.  ESC key will clear screen.
